quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,The beneficent
  55,2,taught the Quran
  55,3,created the human being
  55,4,taught him the speech
  55,5,The sun and the moon with precisely calculated (courses)
  55,6,The herb (or the star) and the tree both humble themselves (before Him)
  55,7,And He raised the sky and set up the balance
  55,8,that you do not outdo the balance
  55,9,And perform the weighing with justice and do not make the scale light
  55,10,And He set up the earth for the human race
  55,11,in it there are fruits and palm trees having coverings
  55,12,"and the seed having outer shell, and the fragrant herbs"
  55,13,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,14,He created the human being from dried clay like pottery clay
  55,15,And He created the Jinn from flame of a fire
  55,16,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,17,Master of the two easts and Master of the two wests
  55,18,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,19,He made the two seas flow freely to meet
  55,20,there is a barrier between them that they do not go beyond
  55,21,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,22,Pearl and coral comes out of both of them
  55,23,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,24,And the sailing ships raised in the sea like the mountains/road signs belong to Him
  55,25,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,26,Everyone on it (the earth) is mortal
  55,27,"while your Master's essence, having the majesty and the nobility remains (forever)"
  55,28,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,29,Everyone in the skies and on the earth ask Him (for their needs). Every day He is in some affair
  55,30,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,31,"We are going to attend to you, the two important beings (humans and Jinn)"
  55,32,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,33,"You, group of Jinn and humans, if you can cross the boundaries of the skies and the earth then cross. You cannot cross except with an authorization"
  55,34,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,35,"A flame of fire and melted copper will be sent upon both of you, and you cannot help/defend yourselves"
  55,36,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,37,And when the sky splits and it becomes red like the red rawhide (or red hot oil)
  55,38,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,39,On that day no human being or Jinn is asked about his sin
  55,40,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,41,"The guilty ones are recognized by their appearance, then they are taken by (the hair lock of) the forehead and the feet"
  55,42,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,43,This is hell that the guilty ones deny it
  55,44,They go around between it and between hot boiling water
  55,45,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,46,And there are two gardens for anyone who fears his Master’s position
  55,47,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,48,Two (gardens) having a variety (of trees)
  55,49,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,50,There are two springs flowing in both of them
  55,51,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,52,There are pairs of every fruits in both of them
  55,53,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,54,"Leaning on cushions/beds inside of which is from heavy silk, and fruits of the two gardens are within reach"
  55,55,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,56,And there are girls with restrained glances in them whom no human being or Jinn had sex with them before them
  55,57,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,58,They are like the ruby and the coral
  55,59,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,60,Is reward of the goodness anything except goodness
  55,61,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,62,And beside those two are two (other) gardens
  55,63,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,64,Both dark green (because of lush vegetation)
  55,65,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,66,There are two springs gushing out in both of them
  55,67,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,68,There are fruits and date and pomegranate in both of them
  55,69,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,70,There are good and beautiful females in both of them
  55,71,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,72,Appealing girls restricted in the pavilions
  55,73,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,74,No human being or Jinn had sex with them before them
  55,75,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,76,Leaning on green pillows and fine colorful carpets
  55,77,Then which of your Master’s favors do you deny
  55,78,"Blessed is the name of your Master, having the majesty and the nobility"